interpretation: The "man walking" card represents movement and progress. It can indicate a new journey or adventure, whether it be physical or metaphorical. This card encourages taking action and moving forward towards your goals, even if the path may be uncertain. Trust in your ability to navigate the unknown and have faith that each step will lead you closer to your destination. Alternatively, this card can suggest restlessness or a need for change. It may be time to break free from stagnant situations and explore new opportunities. Keywords associated with this card include exploration, progress, adventure, action, and restlessness.
